tafsir[2]{c,v,t}:
  39,43,"What! Do they take for intercessors others besides Allah? Say: \"Even if they have no power whatever and no intelligence?\""
  39,46,"Say: \"O Allah! Creator of the heavens and the earth! Knower of all that is hidden and open! it is Thou that wilt judge between Thy Servants in those matters about which they have differed.\""